Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:09.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! That's a convenience store trash can...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:10.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うそ… あれ コンビニのゴミ箱？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, don't go near a guy named Heiwajima Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:12.77,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とにかく 平和島静雄ってヤツには近づくなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:18.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at dealing with Shizu-chan\N because he doesn't listen to words or reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:14.96,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シズちゃんの暴力ってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:18.12,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,理屈も言葉も通じないんだから 苦手だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you never to come to Ikebukuro again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:21.95,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,池袋には二度と来るなって言わなかったっけか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shizuo! Fighting isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:25.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,静雄 ケンカ よくないネ～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.18,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うるせぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? The strongest in Ikebukuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.55,0:01:28.52,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ええ～ 池袋最強？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:30.57,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それならやっぱあいつだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:32.42,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,平和島静雄！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiwajima Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:01:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got fired without any warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:01:59.60,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,会社が急にクビだって！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They told me to leave the dorm as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:01.94,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,寮も出てけって いきなりですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:03.44,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,退職金もなし！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:06.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't get any severance pay, so I can't even afford food or rent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:06.02,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,食費も生活費もあったもんじゃありません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The government won't do anything to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.80,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,国もなんにもしてくれない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's the government! It's all the government's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.04,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,全部 国が悪いんです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:11.47,Secondary Thought,,0,0,0,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:11.03,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うるせぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you go into debt over a hostess?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:15.39,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で 借金して風俗通いかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:16.21,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,愛です！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mint and I truly love each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:19.49,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ミントちゃんと私は本気で愛し合っているんです！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:20.75,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:21.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:21.56,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うぜぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:25.02,Secondary,,0,0,0,,We can only meet at the club and I don't even know her cell number...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:23.00,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お店でしか会えないし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.96,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,携帯の番号も知りません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we are truly in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:27.75,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 僕たちには本当の愛が…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:30.96,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,むかつく！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You only see each other at the club...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:33.33,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,店でしか会わねぇ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't even know her cell number...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.57,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,携帯の番号も知らねぇだぁ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.42,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.51,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お… おい 静雄！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll say this right off...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:38.77,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,最初に言っておく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:40.40,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何が本当の…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:46.10,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,愛だぁ～～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:51.25,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレは暴力が嫌いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:56.13,Chat,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:03:01.40,Chat,,0,0,0,,There's a guy named Heiwajima Shizuo who's\N been going completely out of control recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:01.86,Chat,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:06.58,Chat,,0,0,0,,Is Heiwajima Shizuo that guy who wears a bartender's uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:07.33,Chat,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:11.99,Chat,,0,0,0,,They say he's always been scary, but apparently he's even worse now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:15.54,Chat,,0,0,0,,People are saying Ikebukuro's turned into a battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.37,Chat,,0,0,0,,I've seen him before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:21.97,Chat,,0,0,0,,And Heiwajima Shizuo is indeed scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.12,Chat,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:27.21,Chat,,0,0,0,,I don't think you should judge someone based solely on rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:30.88,Chat,,0,0,0,,Oh, Setton. Is Heiwajima your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.89,Chat,,0,0,0,,Maybe...you're the same as him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:35.73,Chat,,0,0,0,,I'm scared! Someone save me!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:37.11,Chat,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, I can't collect money from anyone if you keep beating them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:39.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ったく…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.98,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どいつもこいつもぶっ飛ばされちゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.76,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,回収になんねぇだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.10,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すんません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:47.91,Thought,,0,0,0,,It reeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.02,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,臭ぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said he hasn't been back for two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.30,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,２～３日前から帰ってねぇとよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has been happening a lot recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.82,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,最近 多いなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because of those fabled human traffickers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.49,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,噂の人間狩りってやつか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,It reeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.58,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,臭ぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, people were injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.69,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おいおい ケガ人出てるじゃねぇかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard it was The Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.46,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,切り裂き魔だってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:15.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ついさっきかよ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it! He ran that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:18.17,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレ見たぜ！ あっちの方に逃げた！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:23.36,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ったく… ブクロもまた騒がしくなってきたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ikebukuro's in an uproar again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,It reeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:29.57,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,臭ぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:38.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the whole town reeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.89,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やっぱり臭ぇ 街中がにおいやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:39.69,Thought,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this smell!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:39.67,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんのにおいだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:41.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ugh, This is annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:40.95,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うぜぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi Shizuo, Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.71,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ハ～イ 静雄 トムさ～ん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Simon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.33,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よう サイモン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shizuo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:48.81,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,静雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, he's been in a bad mood recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:51.79,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すまねぇ 最近機嫌が悪くってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shizuo...he in puberty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.64,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,静雄 思春期か？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's more like his rebellious stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.70,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つうか 反抗期だな～ ありゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:00.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rebalance...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:00.83,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ハンコ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.41,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おう 久しぶりだな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got another leading role, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:22.48,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,また映画の主役ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Hanejima Yuhei, I mean Heiwajima Kasuka, is quite the star.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.83,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大活躍ですね～ 羽島幽平…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:28.63,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや 平和島幽さん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be proud of your younger brother, Mr. Heiwajima Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:35.98,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お兄さんとしても鼻が高いんじゃないですか？ 平和島静雄さん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:42.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, let me introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:42.19,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼 実は 私 こういう者でして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't just look good, he's also a good actor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:47.76,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルックスだけではなく 演技もなかなかのものですからねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, what was the name of his first film, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:52.50,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,デビュー作なんていいましたっけねぇ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vampire Ninjas: Carmilla the Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:58.46,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうそう 「吸血忍者カーミラ才蔵」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew he'd hit it big when I saw him then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:14.12,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのころから大物になると思ってましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:18.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He performed all of his own stunts too, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:17.79,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,確か アクションもスタントなしで こなしてましたよねぇ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to tell me whether or not you helped train him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.72,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お兄さんの指導があったとか なかったとか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:26.39,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日はそのあたりのことについて ぜひお話を…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:30.47,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,静雄！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:45.03,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレは暴力が嫌いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's no lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:46.99,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そいつはうそじゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:50.96,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレだって 初めからこんなだったわけじゃねぇんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.60,0:06:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first time was when I fought with my little brother Kasuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:58.68,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いちばん最初は弟の幽とケンカしたときだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I snapped over something trivial, lifted\N up the fridge and tried to throw it at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.09,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つまんねぇことでキレた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.90,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレは冷蔵庫を持ち上げてぶん投げようとした
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that I thought about lifting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:18.39,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,持ち上がるなんて思ったわけじゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't go without lifting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:22.76,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただ持ち上げずにはいられなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:24.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それから…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shizuo, your butt sounds like a shamisen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:26.99,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,静雄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.83,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お尻 ペンペ～ン！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:30.48,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,バ～カ バ～カ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't control myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:35.68,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,自分を抑えきれねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't angry; my body just moved on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:39.00,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,怒りがわくと 体が勝手に動いちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And whenever that happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.86,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そして その度に…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People can do crazy things in extreme situations, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.97,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,火事場の馬鹿力ってあるでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be what you always use, Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:08.38,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,静雄君はきっと それを常に使えるんじゃないかな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The brain saves that power by destroying a person's muscles and bones when they reach their limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:10.51,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,脳が力をセーブするのは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:14.70,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,限界を超えると 骨や筋肉が破壊されてしまうからなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But your brain makes that power explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:19.45,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも静雄君の脳は力を爆発させてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be the mystery of life: an astonishing event like no other!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.18,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まさに生命の神秘！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:23.14,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,瞠目結舌の驚きだね！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:26.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you let me examine your body just on—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:25.76,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ 君の体 一度検査…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Owowowowow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:28.17,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,痛たたたた！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:31.17,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,痛い！ 痛いよ 静雄君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That hurts, Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't understand the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.06,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,細けぇことは分からねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:33.62,Secondary,,0,0,0,,It's going to break!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I couldn't control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:36.28,Secondary,,0,0,0,,My ulna!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とにかく オレは怒りを抑えられねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd break my body and whatever was around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.48,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そして周りのもんをぶっ壊し
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:38.95,Secondary,,0,0,0,,My right ulna!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.24,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレの体もぶっ壊れる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:42.46,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけは分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:47.76,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そして…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I stopped trying to control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.81,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレは我慢をやめた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no reason to try in the first place if I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:54.26,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうせできねぇなら 初めっからする必要なんざねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My body was going to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:55.92,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,体が壊れる？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.10,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,知ったことか！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My body broke countless times and got stronger with every break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:01.56,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレの体は何度もぶっ壊れた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:03.89,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そしてその度に強くなった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As Shinra would say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.11,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,新羅が言うにゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh, how annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:07.90,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,めんどくせぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I continued to get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.88,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とにかく オレは強くなり続けた！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:13.95,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だけどよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:19.26,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,君… いつも ケガしてるね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're always injured, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:21.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:20.52,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:23.68,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょっと待ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:30.38,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい 牛乳飲んで 強くならないとね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drink some milk so you can grow stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here. You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.88,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい 君にも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.36,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:39.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:39.86,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やっちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when I came to, I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:43.46,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんつうか 気がつくと オレは…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:44.03,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd it turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:52.76,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしてこうなった？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was raised in a normal home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.43,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うちは普通の家庭だった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't suffer any trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.18,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんかトラウマがあるわけでもねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:01.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なのによ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kasuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.48,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,幽…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:04.95,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you...afraid of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:09.96,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前 オレのこと怖くねぇのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:13.67,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,別に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happened when I entered Raira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:29.06,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,来良に入学したころだった…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's our opening anniversary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:32.82,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オープン記念ネ～！ サービスするヨ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything's on special!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:35.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our store's been around forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:38.28,Secondary,,0,0,0,,It seems like we were fated to go to the same high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.70,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,また同じ学校に通えるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:38.08,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんだか運命を感じるね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:39.39,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,黙れ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's your body holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.97,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どう？ その後の体の調子は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, let me examine you to commemorate our reunion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:44.49,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだ 再会の記念に検査を…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:47.55,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ダメ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how about you let me draw some blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:49.97,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ せめて採血だけでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Celty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.29,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,セルティ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd you go yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.09,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日はどうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried because you didn't come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,帰って来ないから心配したよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you looking for your head again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.45,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,また 首を捜してたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You say that, but I bet you met a nice guy—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:05.09,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなこと言って どこかにいい人ができたんじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Celty...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.05,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,セルティ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop poking my solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.32,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,地味にみぞおち突っつくのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Celty, let me introduce you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:14.96,Secondary,,0,0,0,,An odd feeling came over me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:14.94,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんて言っていいのか分かんねぇけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's my friend, Heiwajima Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.99,Secondary,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to say it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:18.11,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,「こいつは…」って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shizuo, Celty lives with me, or I should say she's my future—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.84,Secondary,,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:21.14,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,将来の…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:22.53,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,変な感じがした
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a horrible memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:26.84,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,嫌なこと思い出しちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, that was about the same time I met that pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:33.43,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだ そうだった… あのノミ虫野郎がオレの前に現れたのもあのころだった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that person...is Orihara Izaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:42.20,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あいつが… 折原臨也がよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:02.62,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あいつのことは…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Orihara Izaya from my middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.63,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,中学で一緒だった 折原臨也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.87,Secondary,,0,0,0,,...I hated him from the first time I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he's not that good a person...maybe I should say he's a horrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:07.57,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,見た瞬間から気に入らなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.42,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,かなり嫌なヤツ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so mean, Shinra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.34,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ひどいなぁ 新羅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mean it in a bad way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.72,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いやいや 悪い意味じゃなくって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:15.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:15.42,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,気に入らねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:16.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:25.65,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,残念 君となら 楽しめると思うんだけどなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:25.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I could have some fun with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:26.84,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うるせぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:29.90,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなこと言わないでさ 静雄君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See...this is fun, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.70,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら 楽しいだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The day we met...we tried to fight to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:51.83,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,会ったその日 オレと臨也は殺し合いのケンカをした
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a reason why. I just didn't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:55.92,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,理由なんかねぇ ただ気に入らなかっただけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:55.92,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でもよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.26,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫ですか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:07.45,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫 大丈夫 彼 頑丈にできてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's built strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he...really alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.51,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほ… 本当に大丈夫なんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:13.27,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫 大丈夫 ご苦労さん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:16.49,Thought,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:19.50,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ… しくじっちまった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:19.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:30.93,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,奇遇だねぇ 臨也も来てるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Izaya's here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why aren't you injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.69,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つうか なんで無傷なわけ～？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:40.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you! I'll kill you! I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:40.48,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,殺す 殺す 殺す！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:39.54,Secondary,,0,0,0,,The next day was an annoying one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:38.67,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,次の日からうぜぇ日々が始まった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guys I had never seen before were fighting me one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:46.26,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,次から次へと 訳の分かんねぇ連中がケンカを売ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hadn't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.86,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレはなんにもしてねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just living peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:50.78,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただ静かに暮らしてぇだけなのによ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Dammit! Dammit! Dammit! What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:57.08,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,くそっ！ くそっ！ くそっ！くっそ～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:57.96,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,むかつく！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:15:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How annoying! Annoying! Annoying! Annoying! Annoying! Annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:15:03.09,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うぜぇ うぜぇ うぜぇ うぜぇ うぜぇ うぜぇ！ うぜぇ～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:12.48,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:20.88,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,死ね～～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Izaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:43.30,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,臨也だ 臨也の野郎が裏で糸を引いてやがったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Izaya was pulling all the strings behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when I found that out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:44.94,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そいつを知ったオレは…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,IIIzaaayaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:47.31,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,い～ざ～や～!!\
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only I'd killed him then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:53.06,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここでヤツを殺しておけばよぉ！ くそっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After graduating from Raira...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.94,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,来良を卒業してから…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:15:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:01.04,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どう？ 似合う？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do I look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The idiot kept on living like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.36,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,バカはこんな感じで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that pest was doing something with the yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:06.57,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ノミ虫はヤクザとつるんで 何かやってた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it was quiet for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:09.73,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とにかくしばらくは静かだった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:11.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:11.61,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でもって オレは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acted that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:29.12,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,てな感じで どういうわけか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:34.18,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いらっしゃい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:39.10,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おい 見たか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.22,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うそだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the actor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.46,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら 俳優の… 羽島幽平だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanejima Yuhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo, Kasuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:48.24,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よう 幽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:49.45,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしたんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:16:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bartender uniforms?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.12,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,バーテン服？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think you should change jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:03.38,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あまり仕事は替えない方がいいと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bought a lot for you...so you can continue doing what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:09.20,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつまでも続けられるように たくさん買っておいた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:11.90,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:13.66,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まっ 頑張ってみるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.09,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それが…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:19.42,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,く… くっそ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:31.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Izaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.43,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,臨也ぁ～～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got framed by that pest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:33.73,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ノミ虫野郎にはめられちまって…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and he disappeared from Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:38.22,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ヤツはブクロから姿を消した
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They soon found out I was innocent and released me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:41.69,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレもすぐに無実と分かって 釈放された
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:42.82,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,けど…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:47.01,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...I didn't keep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:46.80,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,悪ぃ 約束 守れなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, if it isn't Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:48.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おっ 静雄じゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tom was a class ahead of me in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:57.20,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,トムさんはオレの中学の先輩で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He asked me to help him collect debts from people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:18:00.16,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,借金の回収業を手伝えって言ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To sum it up, I'm his bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:03.25,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まっ 要は用心棒ってわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't like it at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.29,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,初めは気が乗らなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tom would say...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:06.52,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,トムさんは…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You don't have to raise your hand to her like that."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:09.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,別に無理に手ぇ上げるこたぁねぇって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"By the way, Heiwajima Shizuo's with me."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:12.62,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ブクロで平和島静雄って聞きゃあよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"No one can stand in his way."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.94,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,逆らうヤツもそういねぇよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...stuff like that, but Kasuka got busy\N ever since then and I hadn't seen him since.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.17,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つってくれたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:21.52,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんつうか そのころから幽のヤツ忙しくなっちまって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.95,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれっきり会えてなかったからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:29.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's mad at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:28.13,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あいつ 怒ってっかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:30.16,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:34.66,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,幽平～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:42.40,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,格好いい～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuhei, this way, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.69,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,幽平さ～ん お願いしま～す！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:59.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't understand why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:02.17,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんだか分かんねぇが 気が楽になった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...but I felt better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm still working with Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:06.32,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でもって オレは今もトムさんと働いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Repayment deadline?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:08.71,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,返済期限～？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't understand difficult stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:11.12,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,難しいこと分っかんな～い
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We march to our own beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:12.74,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレたちゆとりだしぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly. School, society, everyone's to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:16.49,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうそう 学校 社会 み～んな悪いの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're the heart of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.37,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,心の闇だっつうの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:20.58,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのなぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:22.70,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分っかんねぇっつってんの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.64,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,消えろ おっさん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.48,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おっさんもお仕事なんでな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What's with the stare?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:29.12,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんだよ その目は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why're you wearing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.88,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おい！ 何 その格好？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot, he's a butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.98,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,バ～カ 執事だよ 執事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:38.34,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前ら 静雄のこと知らねぇのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't know who Shizuo is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:39.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:41.10,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,誰 それ？ 有名人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some famous person?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true, butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:43.08,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうなの？ 執事さん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.99,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ぶはっ！ 吹いた～！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I spit it all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:48.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you be so kind as to bring me another one, butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:48.60,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おかわり持ってきてくださいませんこと？執事さ～ん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.89,0:19:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You certainly do march to your own beat if \Nyou're in Ikebukuro and don't know about Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.38,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ブクロにいて 静雄を知らねぇとは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:53.63,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,確かにゆとりだわな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:02.03,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレの服を… 弟からもらった服を…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clothes my brother gave me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, I really don't like violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:13.19,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それでも やっぱり暴力は好きじゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:15.69,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレはもっと強くなりてぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Strong enough to control my rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:19.89,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,自分の怒りを抑えられるほど強くな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel much better after talking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:25.12,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,な～んか お前と話してたらす～っとしてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:30.14,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうか よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd been irritated this whole time. I didn't know why, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:33.70,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここんとこ ずっとイライラしててよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:35.36,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,訳分かんねぇんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.41,0:20:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard about that and was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:40.34,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ そんな噂を聞いて 気になっていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? Sorry to make you worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:42.02,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そっか 悪ぃな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:43.33,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,気ぃ遣わせちまって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pffft. Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:55.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うるせぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:57.45,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I want to put distance between\N strangers and myself, I can't stand being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:01.59,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,他人と距離を取りてぇくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:03.25,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一人じゃいられねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I always try to connect with people like Tom or Kasuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:05.71,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから誰かとつながろうとしちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.44,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,トムさんや 幽と…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a lot like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:14.39,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あいつはオレと似てるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She must have someone as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:19.19,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あいつもきっと誰かを…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shizuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:37.59,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,静雄～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:40.03,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,思春期 終わったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you done with puberty?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then eat sushi. Sushi's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:42.38,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ スシ食うネ スシはイイよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:43.75,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ウマイよ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.68,0:21:45.70,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,またな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.72,Thought,,0,0,0,,Izaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:15.92,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,臨也…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:19.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,That's it! I thought it reeked here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:16.76,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:20.96,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,臭ぇ臭ぇと思ったら… お前の！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:21.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.08,0:22:26.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.41,0:22:25.50,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何をしている？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:28.49,Thought,,0,0,0,,What is he planning to do in this city now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.14,0:22:28.51,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この街で 今度は何をするつもりだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:37.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:44.79,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,くっそぉ～～!! い～ざ～や～～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,IIIzaaayaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.10,0:24:19.72,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an8}制作：LASTZZZ 安静の云 akira アキラ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.17,0:24:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:16.90,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は夢を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.77,0:24:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same dream over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.06,0:24:18.86,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,繰り返し 同じ夢を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm asleep when it's awake,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.47,0:24:22.08,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,向こうが目覚めているとき 私は眠り
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.88,0:24:24.87,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}{\an8}漫游字幕组\N{\fnKartika}http://popgo.net/bbs/
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.17,0:24:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and it's asleep when I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.29,0:24:26.32,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私が目覚めているとき 向こうは目を閉じているのだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.39,0:24:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Time: Fleeting Dreams.
